1. *Nosi* ga je kroz vrt u parku. (He was carrying it through the garden to the park.)
2. *Nosio* je knjigu čitavu godinu. (He was carrying the book for an entire year.)
3. Kao da je *nosila* malo dete. (It was like she was carrying a little child.)
4. *Nose* li ti čizme u školu? (Do you wear your boots to school?)
5. *Nosim* li ja kaput čak i u ljetno vrijeme? (Do I wear a coat even in the summertime?)